snippet.title: Hymn to the Earless God Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
New RPG from the creator of Jimmy and the Pulsating Mass!  Our Kickstarter was successful--thank you so much!

Wishlist and check out the demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2165130/Hymn_to_the_Earless_God

Don't have Steam?  Try the demo on itch.io:
https://housekeepinggames.itch.io/hymn-to-the-earless-god

Talk about the game on Discord:
https://discord.gg/A9sbH53

Follow us on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/KaseyOzymy
